ratbox-services installation guide
----------------------------------

1. Run the configure script.  If you wish to install it to a different 
   directory than the default /usr/local/ratbox-services, include the
   --prefix option.

   eg, ./configure --prefix=/home/user/services

2. Edit include/config.h

3. Run make

4. Run make install

5. Change to the directory it installed to, edit example.conf and save it
   as the filename specified in CONF_PATH in config.h, default rserv.conf

6. Run ./rserv
